  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Validity and Reliability of a Wearable System for Assessing Turning Characteristics.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Subjects are reclaimed to finish several turning task under different turning angle.

      The wearable system is patched on both subjects' legs and waist, to assess turning
      characteristics under different turning angle.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
